 "timestamp": "2026-04-23T13:47:24Z",
 "wikitext": "{{DISPLAYTITLE:<span style=\"font-family: Alata;color: #fc0303; text-shadow: 1px 3px 0 #fc7b03, 1px 9px 5px #fcf403\">Object 46: Sensitive Candies</span>}}__NOTOC__\n{{CSS|content=@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Alata%7CAlata');}}\n<div style=\"background-color:#fc7b03; color: white; margin:1em; padding:5px 10px; border:5px solid red; border-radius: 3px\">\n==<span style=\"font-family: Alata;color: #fc0303; text-shadow: 1px 3px 0 #fc7b03, 1px 9px 5px #fcf403\"> Description </span>==\n{{Blurimage|file=Sweets!.jpg|caption=Sensitive Candies.}}\n<span style=\"font-family: Alata;><big>'''Sensitive Candies''' are multi-colored sweets coated in layers of white sugar, widely used throughout <span style=\"color:#fc0303\">[[The Backrooms|<span style=\"color:#fc0303\">The Backrooms</span>]]</span>. They are easily portable, usually weighing less than 5 grams.</big></span>\n\n<span style=\"font-family: Alata;><big>Their distinctive minty smell distinguishes them from other candies with similar appearances. Upon consuming them, all of one's senses may be strengthened for an hour, including vision and hearing.</big></span>\n==<span style=\"font-family: Alata;color: #fc0303; text-shadow: 1px 3px 0 #fc7b03, 1px 9px 5px #fcf403\"> Usage </span>==\n<span style=\"font-family: Alata;><big>Studies have shown eating them can lead to keen eyesight, allowing acute perception and observation; sharper hearing, allowing one to hear outside of normal human auditory range; and faster precognition, allowing one to avoid dangerous locations.</big></span>\n\n<span style=\"font-family: Alata;><big>Due to this, explorers commonly carry 3-5 candies to strengthen their senses, helping them to sense and evade danger quickly. This is extremely useful during explorations and investigations, where one is required to stay in dangerous places for a long time.</big></span>\n\n<span style=\"font-family: Alata;><big>However, studies find these candies to reduce stamina, increase pain sensitivity, and raise blood pressure, leading to a future increased risk of heart disease. As a result, wanderers must use it sparingly or only in dire situations to mitigate the side-effects.</big></span>\n==<span style=\"font-family: Alata;color: #fc0303; text-shadow: 1px 3px 0 #fc7b03, 1px 9px 5px #fcf403\"> Locations </span>==\n<span style=\"font-family: Alata;><big>'''Sensitive Candies''' can be found occasionally in levels with moderate entity count, such as [[Level 7|<span style=\"color:#fc0303\">Level 7</span>]] and [[Level 948|<span style=\"color:#fc0303\">Level 948</span>]]. They can appear anywhere in those levels on any surface, sometimes jarringly, making them stand out among other objects.</big></span>\n\n<span style=\"font-family: Alata;><big>These candies are found to appear in places where a person intends to return to. Additionally, they only do so when the person is unaware of it, preventing one from exploiting.</big></span>\n==<span style=\"font-family: Alata;color: #fc0303; text-shadow: 1px 3px 0 #fc7b03, 1px 9px 5px #fcf403\"> Discovery & Origin </span>==\n<span style=\"font-family: Alata;><big>'''Sensitive Candies''' were discovered by a wanderer in 2010, who reported them to the [[M.E.G.|<span style=\"color:#fc0303\">M.E.G.</span>]] after experiencing their magical effects.</big></span>\n\n<span style=\"font-family: Alata;><big>Despite being known, studied, and utilized for more than a decade, the true origin of these candies remains unknown to this day.</big></span>\n\n{{Collapse|initial=<span style=\"font-family: Alata;color: #fc0303; text-shadow: 1px 3px 0 #fc7b03, 1px 9px 5px #fcf403\"><big>'''Open Author and Licensing Information'''</big></span><br>|final=<span style=\"font-family: Alata;color: #fc0303; text-shadow: 1px 3px 0 #fc7b03, 1px 9px 5px #fcf403\"><big>'''Close Author and Licensing Information'''</big></span>|num=1|body=<span style=\"font-family: Alata;\"><big>Written by [[User:Brightened Star|<span style=\"color:#fc0303\">Brightened Star</span>]].<br>The image is from [https://pixnio.com/food-and-drink/desserts-cakes/sugared-jubes-in-orange-bowl# <span style=\"color:#fc0303\">Leon Brooks</span>] on pixnio.com.</big></span>{{User:Brightened Star/Credits|code=<span style=\"font-family: Alata;color: #fc0303; text-shadow: 1px 3px 0 #fc7b03, 1px 9px 5px #fcf403\"><big>|codeend=</big></span><br>|initial=Click for more pages by [[User:Brightened Star|<span style=\"color:#fc0303\">Brightened Star</span>]] (Including collabs)|final=Click to hide pages by [[User:Brightened Star|<span style=\"color:#fc0303\">Brightened Star</span>]] (Including collabs)}}}}</div>[[Category:Objects]][[Category:Food]]"
